Product_Description: Key Features QLED Vision Pro+ : Elevate your viewing experience and get closer to reality like never before with 94 % color gamut 4K Ultra HD : UHD resolution refers to 3840 pixels x 2160 pixels bifurcation of the LED Screen, which is around 4 times higher than full HD TVs; and results in an ultra- sharp picture quality. 4K Upscaler : A UHD Upscaler upgrades FHD signal to near-4K quality to deliver powerful details, allowing viewers to enjoy 4K picture quality even with FHD signal.
